{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Driver.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.run\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">run</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">goal</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Goal\">Meta.Grind.Goal</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">ctx</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Context\">Context</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">scope</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Scope\">Scope</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">stepLimit?</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a></span> := <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option.none\">none</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.GrindM\">Meta.Grind.GrindM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Driver.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Result\">Result</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Generate verification conditions for a goal of the form `P ⊢ₛ wp⟦e⟧ Q s₁ ... sₙ` by repeatedly\ndecomposing `e` using registered `@[spec]` theorems.\nReturn the VCs and invariant goals.\n\n`stepLimit?`, when `some n`, seeds the fuel counter to `n`; when `none`, fuel is unlimited.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Driver.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.run","kind":"def","line":152,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.run","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Driver.lean#L152-L171"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Driver.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Result.inlineHandledInvariants\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">Result</span>.<span class=\"name\">inlineHandledInvariants</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Driver.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Result\">Result</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Std/Data/HashSet/Basic.html#Std.HashSet\">Std.HashSet</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Invariant numbers handled inline by `Driver.emitVC`. Used by `Frontend` to\navoid spurious \"alt does not match any invariant\" warnings for inline-consumed\nalts. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Driver.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Result.inlineHandledInvariants","kind":"def","line":150,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Result.inlineHandledInvariants","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Driver.lean#L150-L150"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Driver.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Result.vcs\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">Result</span>.<span class=\"name\">vcs</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Driver.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Result\">Result</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Goal\">Meta.Grind.Goal</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Unassigned VCs. Each shares the parent `Grind.Goal`'s state. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Driver.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Result.vcs","kind":"def","line":146,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Result.vcs","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Driver.lean#L146-L146"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Driver.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Result.invariants\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">Result</span>.<span class=\"name\">invariants</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Driver.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Result\">Result</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"All invariant goals emitted during VC generation, in emit order. The MVarId at\nindex `i` carries tag `inv{i+1}`, so callers can treat the array index as the\ninvariant number. Some entries may already be assigned (inline-elaborated by\n`Driver.emitVC`); the caller is responsible for filtering before discharging. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Driver.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Result.invariants","kind":"def","line":144,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Result.invariants","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Driver.lean#L144-L144"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Driver.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Result.mk\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">Result</span>.<span class=\"name\">mk</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">Lean.MVarId</a></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Goal\">Lean.Meta.Grind.Goal</a></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Std/Data/HashSet/Basic.html#Std.HashSet\">Std.HashSet</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a></span> → <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Driver.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Result\">Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Result</a></span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Driver.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Result.mk","kind":"ctor","line":139,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Result.mk","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Driver.lean#L139-L150"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">structure</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Driver.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Result\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">Result</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Driver.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Result","kind":"structure","line":139,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Result","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Driver.lean#L139-L150"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Driver.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.work\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">work</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">scope</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Scope\">Scope</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">goal</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Goal\">Meta.Grind.Goal</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGenM\">VCGenM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Unit\">Unit</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Driver.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.work","kind":"def","line":104,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.work","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Driver.lean#L104-L137"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Driver.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.emitVC\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">emitVC</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">goal</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Goal\">Meta.Grind.Goal</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGenM\">VCGenM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Unit\">Unit</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Called when decomposing the goal further did not succeed; in this case we emit a VC for the goal.\nInvariant subgoals are handled separately by `handleInvariantSubgoals` directly inside `work`,\nso they never reach this path.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Driver.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.emitVC","kind":"def","line":81,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.emitVC","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Driver.lean#L81-L98"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Driver.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.elabInvariant\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">elabInvariant</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">invariantAlts</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Std/Data/HashMap/Basic.html#Std.HashMap\">Std.HashMap</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Syntax\">Syntax</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">n</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">mv</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.SymM\">Meta.Sym.SymM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Try to elaborate the user's invariant alt for invariant number `n` inline,\ndischarging `mv` if successful. Looks up `Context.invariantAlts[n]?` (pre-parsed\nin `Frontend`) and dispatches to `exact $rhs` for bullet form or\n`rename_i $args*; exact $rhs` for labelled form. Returns whether elaboration\nsucceeded. Numbering is 1-based; out-of-order labelled forms (e.g. `| inv2 => …`\nbefore `| inv1 => …`) are supported because the map is keyed by parsed number,\nnot position.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Driver.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.elabInvariant","kind":"def","line":27,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.elabInvariant","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Driver.lean#L27-L59"}}],"imports":["Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Context","Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Solve","Lean.Elab.Tactic.Meta","Lean.Meta.Sym.Grind"],"instances":[],"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Driver"}